======================================================================
INPUT FILE FOR TAYLOR-GREEN VORTEX Re=1600, N=256
======================================================================
256 256 256     dimensions of the grid
----------------------------------------------------------------------
000000          ITMIN    first timestep (0 = new simulation)
999999          ITMAX    last timestep
100             IPRNT1   how often to calculate statistics
999999          IPRNT2   how often to write restart files
999999          IWRITE4  how often to write real*4 binary files
----------------------------------------------------------------------
10.0            TMAX     the maximum simulation time
100.0 0         TRESCALE, NRESCALE  rescale time and # of rescales
0.0             TSCALAR  time when to start moving scalars
----------------------------------------------------------------------
0               ITYPV    flow type: 0=decay
----------------------------------------------------------------------
1600.0          RE       Reynolds number (1/viscosity)
-0.001          DT       timestep (negative = fixed dt)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
-1              ISPCV1   Initial spectrum type (-1 = Taylor-Green!)
4               mv1      initial infrared exponent (unused for TG)
2.0             wm0v1    initial peak wavenumber (unused for TG)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
1               force_type    (unused for decay)
2               KFMAX         (unused for decay)
0.5             FAMP          (unused for decay)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
0               dealias (0: 2/3-rule, 1: phase shift + truncation)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
0               det_rand
67748937.       RN1
93712139.       RN2
10765397.       RN3
----------------------------------------------------------------------
0               np, number of Lagrangian particles
1               particle_tracking mechanism
0.1             time_p
0.3             particle_filter_size
----------------------------------------------------------------------
0               les_model (0=none)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
0               nums, # of passive scalars
----------------------------------------------------------------------
======================================================================
